'''托馬斯·康拉德·「湯姆」·哈伐令'''（{{lang-en|Thomas Conrad "Tom" Hoefling}}；{{bd|1960年|12月20日|}}），是一名美國活動家與政治家。他是[[美國的黨|美國的黨]]的創立人與全國主席<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.messengernews.net/page/content.detail/id/519093.html?nav=5010 | title=America’s Independent Party holds caucus meeting | work=[[Fort_Dodge_Messenger|Fort Dodge Messenger]] | date=October 7, 2009 | accessdate=March 8, 2012 | author=Schmit, Ian | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120707185532/http://www.messengernews.net/page/content.detail/id/519093.html?nav=5010 | archivedate=2012年7月7日 | df= }}</ref>，並為該黨[[2012年美国总统选举|2012年]]及[[2016年美国总统选举|2016年美国总统选举]]的[[美國總統|總統候選人]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ballot-access.org/2012/02/29/alan-keyes-party-qualifies-for-florida-ballot/ | title=Alan Keyes’ Party Qualifies for Florida Ballot | work=[[Ballot_Access_News|Ballot Access News]] | date=February 29, 2012 | accessdate=March 8, 2012 | archive-date=2016-05-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160501130107/http://ballot-access.org/2012/02/29/alan-keyes-party-qualifies-for-florida-ballot/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.independentpoliticalreport.com/2012/03/tom-hoefling-is-the-americas-party-presidential-nominee/#comments | title=Tom Hoefling is the America’s Party Presidential Nominee | work=Independent Political Report | date=March 7, 2012 | accessdate=March 8, 2012 | archive-date=2016-10-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161012135638/http://independentpoliticalreport.com/2012/03/tom-hoefling-is-the-americas-party-presidential-nominee/#comments | dead-url=no }}</ref>；亦曾擔任{{le|艾倫·凱斯|Alan Keyes}}的政治團體「美國復興」之政治部主任<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2009/01/18/politics/politico/main4731850.shtml | title=Obama Naysayers Speak Out | work=[[CBS_News|CBS News]] | date=June 26, 2009 | accessdate=March 8, 2012 | archive-date=2011-01-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110131032748/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2009/01/18/politics/politico/main4731850.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>，並以此職銜出任美國保守聯盟的代表<ref>{{cite web | url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=PbIyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=N_IDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6865,2774385&dq=tom-hoefling&hl=en | title=Flap continues over controversial voter guide | work=[[The_Spokesman-Review|The Spokesman-Review]] | date=May 14, 2000 | accessdate=March 8, 2012 | author=Warbis, Mark | archive-date=2017-01-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170115211737/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=PbIyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=N_IDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6865,2774385&dq=tom-hoefling&hl=en | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==活動==
哈伐令分別在2012年8月<ref name="Winger">{{cite news|url=http://www.ballot-access.org/2012/08/11/american-independent-party-picks-tom-hoefling-for-president/|title=Ballot Access News  » Blog Archive   » American Independent Party Picks Tom Hoefling for President|last=Winger|first=Richard|publisher=[[Ballot_Access_News|Ballot Access News]]|accessdate=18 August 2012|archive-date=2016-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160718134742/http://ballot-access.org/2012/08/11/american-independent-party-picks-tom-hoefling-for-president/|dead-url=no}}</ref>及2016年6月<ref>{{cite news |last= Abrams |first= Abigail |title= Don't Like Donald Trump Or Hillary Clinton? Here Are Your Third-Party Options For 2016 |date= 2016-06-08 |website= [[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]] |url= http://www.ibtimes.com/dont-donald-trump-or-hillary-clinton-here-are-your-third-party-options-2016-2379598 |accessdate= 2016-08-04 |quote= American Independent Party:  This ultraconservative party opposes abortion and same-sex marriage, and wants to build a fence along the whole U.S. border. Its presidential nominee in 2016 is Tom Hoefling. |archive-date= 2016-08-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160820220929/http://www.ibtimes.com/dont-donald-trump-or-hillary-clinton-here-are-your-third-party-options-2016-2379598 |dead-url= no }}</ref>被{{le|美國人獨立黨|American Independent Party}}提名為總統候選人。

